1
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,040
Ning.

2
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,239
Look at this.

3
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,319
"Kill Ning Chen,

4
00:01:43,959 --> 00:01:46,760
and 50,000 taels of gold shall be yours."

5
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:51,879
Is that all I am worth?

6
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,719
You old dog.

7
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:58,640
You had best confess everything now.

8
00:01:59,159 --> 00:02:00,879
Who exactly was sending you these letters?

9
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,079
If I am in a good mood,

10
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,879
I might just spare your wretched life.

11
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,479
Let me take a guess.

12
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,240
The Beilin Pass supervisor,

13
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:19,280
Kong Yongchun, am I right?

14
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:20,840
You...

15
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:23,879
How could you possibly guess?

16
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:25,680
Intuition.

17
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:30,919
Move, move.

18
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:31,560
Keep up.

19
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,319
Hurry.

20
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,039
Go.

21
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,400
Chenzi.

22
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:38,800
We found them.

23
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:41,800
Proof of Kong Yongchun's treason.

24
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:55,400
Tell me,

25
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,199
why is it like this?

26
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,039
Why?

27
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,039
Since I joined the Inspectorate,

28
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,159
I have executed the Imperial Uncle,

29
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:06,400
captured bandits,

30
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,000
and quelled foreign threats.

31
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,879
Daxuan is beset by threats on all sides.

32
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:14,000
Men of ambition are blocked at every turn,

33
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,199
yet corrupt officials run rampant.

34
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:21,360
To serve this country and its people,

35
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:23,800
why is it so difficult?

36
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:25,879
Of course it is.

37
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,800
People always think of themselves first.

38
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,360
"Every man for himself, or face destruction."

39
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,960
Once a man is blinded by self-interest,

40
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,680
he can see nothing else.

41
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:42,879
Then I shall turn this world upside down.

42
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,120
Pass the order.

43
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,800
Take inventory of the spoils.

44
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,879
Burn the enemy's provisions.

45
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,840
Signal General Liang.

46
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,719
We will strike them with a counterattack.

47
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,120
Yes, sir.

48
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:08,319
Report, General!

49
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,120
Flames are rising behind the enemy camp.

50
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,280
Their forces are in chaos.

51
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:16,839
Excellent.

52
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,439
It seems young Ning Chen has succeeded.

53
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:20,720
Pass the order to the three armies.

54
00:04:21,319 --> 00:04:22,360
Open the gates and meet the enemy.

55
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,600
All forces, attack!

56
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:25,680
Yes, sir!

57
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:39,560
I... I...

58
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,079
S-Sir...

59
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:52,879
Take him away.

60
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,600
General Liang.

61
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:58,600
Well done.

62
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,439
Excellent work.

63
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,120
A brilliant job.

64
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:01,360
Are you injured?

65
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,040
General, all is well.

66
00:05:03,399 --> 00:05:04,079
I have fulfilled my mission.

67
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,839
You are truly wise and brave, General.

68
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,600
King Zuoting has been captured alive.

69
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,839
He is now in prison.

70
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,040
Everything awaits your decision, General.

71
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:12,920
Good.

72
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,199
The young are truly formidable.

73
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:17,439
And you yielded the military credit to me.

74
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:20,240
Today I will hold a victory feast for you.

75
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:20,839
Come.

76
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,399
General.

77
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:23,399
The victory banquet can wait.

78
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,720
General, please look at these.

79
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:30,360
I found these at the royal court of Zuodu.

80
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,399
King Zuoting can serve as a witness.

81
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:35,120
The chief culprit is Kong Yongchun.

82
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:37,439
He caused not only General Xie's death,

83
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,279
but also murdered five other officers.

84
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:41,480
Outrageous!

85
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:45,199
These were all fine warriors of Daxuan.

86
00:05:45,319 --> 00:05:46,560
Each one valiant and skilled in battle.

87
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:47,879
Defenders of Daxuan.

88
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:49,319
Who would have thought,

89
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:53,560
they would die at the hands of their own.

90
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,000
Chenzi.

91
00:05:59,279 --> 00:05:59,759
Kneel down.

92
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,480
Stay on your knees.

93
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,720
Chenzi, you guessed exactly right.

94
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:04,759
This wretch is guilty of high treason.

95
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,800
I caught him red-handed.

96
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,720
You beast!

97
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:13,279
As an appointed official of Daxuan,

98
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:14,959
you dared to collude with foreign enemies,

99
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,399
and murder the generals of Daxuan.

100
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,160
You...

101
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:20,000
Has your conscience been eaten by dogs?

102
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:22,079
General Liang, please calm yourself.

103
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:32,839
Supervisor Kong.

104
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:34,720
Does this look familiar?

105
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:37,399
I...

106
00:06:37,879 --> 00:06:39,199
I have no idea what you are talking about.

107
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,680
Secret letters you wrote to King Zuoting.

108
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:44,560
You do not even remember them?

109
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,879
Death is upon you, yet you still deny it?

110
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,279
Kong Yongchun.

111
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:50,240
Ning Chen has led his troops

112
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,079
and breached the Northern Capital court.

113
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:53,600
and captured King Zuoting alive.

114
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:55,160
These secret letters

115
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:57,879
were found in King Zuoting's royal tent.

116
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,040
You beast!

117
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:01,920
You deserve to be cut a thousand times!

118
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,959
It is fine if you refuse to confess.

119
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:08,560
Once we return to the capital,

120
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:12,079
King Zuoting will reveal it all himself.

121
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:14,480
When that time comes,

122
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,959
let His Majesty render judgment.

123
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:19,720
Guards!

124
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:22,360
Follow me to raid the Supervisor's home.

125
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:24,639
Detain all those involved.

126
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,680
Let His Majesty judge them in the capital.

127
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:27,600
Yes, sir!

128
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,120
Get up.

129
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,600
Move.

130
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,560
Old Kong,

131
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:44,000
why bring this upon yourself?

132
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,759
We barely even know each other.

133
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:48,360
Why spend so much money to buy my head?

134
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,079
Do you have too much money to burn?

135
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,279
Even if you stay silent, I already know.

136
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:58,319
The Left Chancellor is behind you, right?

137
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,040
The murder of those six soldiers,

138
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,600
the Left Chancellor did that, did he not?

139
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:05,800
Actually,

140
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:06,680
brother,

141
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,680
we are actually on the same side.

142
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,120
The Left Chancellor and I are sworn foes.

143
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,959
Everything I have done

144
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:15,199
was to bring down the Left Chancellor.

145
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:19,319
You only have a few days left to live.

146
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:20,480
How about

147
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,439
I let you in on a little secret?

148
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,240
You surely know

149
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:26,319
how I executed the Imperial Uncle, right?

150
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,480
But you surely do not know

151
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,560
how, after slaying the Imperial Uncle,

152
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,200
I faced no consequences at all.

153
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,720
That is because I

154
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,480
am the Emperor's illegitimate son.

155
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:42,759
You have no idea

156
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,440
the daily exhaustion of being a bastard.

157
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:46,039
That wretched old Left Chancellor

158
00:08:46,279 --> 00:08:48,559
schemes day and night to kill me.

159
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,799
How about you help me,

160
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:51,919
and I help you?

161
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:54,399
Prove the Left Chancellor's treason to me.

162
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,879
When I defeat the Left Chancellor and rise,

163
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,480
I will go before my father,

164
00:08:58,679 --> 00:08:59,840
put in a few good words for you,

165
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,519
play the affectionate son a bit,

166
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:02,120
and perhaps if the old man is in a good mood,

167
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,480
he will set you free.

168
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:14,039
Since you refuse to talk,

169
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,480
then I cannot help you.

170
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,120
However, old Kong,

171
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:20,360
Your crime condemns your nine generations.

172
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,039
Think it over carefully.

173
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:24,080
Your father, your mother,

174
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:24,919
your uncle,

175
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,840
your eldest sister-in-law,

176
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,559
your children,

177
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:27,200
your wife.

178
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,519
Oh, that's right,

179
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,200
I forgot to tell you some good news.

180
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:33,600
Your beautiful wife

181
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,159
will not have to die.

182
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,440
Do you still remember

183
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,120
that fat oaf who captured you?

184
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:40,279
The one shaped like this.

185
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:43,159
He has taken a fancy to your wife.

186
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,879
Love at first sight, you might say.

187
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,679
What did he just say?

188
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:51,559
"Spring breeze longs to cross Yumen Pass,

189
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:56,120
seven times a night and not in vain."

190
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,799
That vile fat scoundrel

191
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,840
is already on his way to your home.

192
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,600
How can you all be so shameless?

193
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:07,519
You flatter us, old Kong.

194
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,240
Think it over carefully.

195
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,399
If you change your mind,

196
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,399
I will mount up at once

197
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,879
and chase that fat brute back for you.

198
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,039
Perhaps there is still time.

199
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:16,240
Call me when you have decided.

200
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:17,759
Wait.

201
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:19,879
Do you mean what you say?

202
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,240
I am a man

203
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,480
who never jokes.

204
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,720
Besides, you can only trust me now,

205
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:35,000
and trust my father.

206
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:39,320
The Left Chancellor's secret letters,

207
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:41,879
they are all in the capital now.

208
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,200
The capital?

209
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,879
Should they not be burned after reading?

210
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:48,720
What the Left Chancellor ordered me to do,

211
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,120
the crimes I committed,

212
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:53,600
were all capital crimes of treason.

213
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,440
I knew far too much.

214
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,879
I feared that one day

215
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,320
he would kill me to silence me.

216
00:10:59,879 --> 00:11:00,639
And so

217
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,919
I sent men

218
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,399
to deliver these secret letters

219
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,639
in secret to the capital.

220
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:09,000
If anything ever happened to me,

221
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,120
these secret letters

222
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,480
would be sent to the Inspectorate.

223
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,639
I never imagined, however,

224
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,799
that in the end

225
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,879
I would fall into your hands.

226
00:11:21,279 --> 00:11:23,000
You are quite clever, are you not?

227
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,039
What was the matter earlier?

228
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:24,919
Did you drink bad wine?

229
00:11:25,399 --> 00:11:26,759
The wine at Beilin Pass is too strong,

230
00:11:26,919 --> 00:11:27,360
is it not?

231
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,279
Where in the capital are they kept?

232
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:31,080
The west market outside the city,

233
00:11:31,519 --> 00:11:32,679
the Liu family cloth shop.

234
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,080
I have told you everything I should.

235
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,960
Hurry and stop that vile fat scoundrel,

236
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,519
go and intercept him!

237
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,399
A lovestruck fool.

238
00:11:42,559 --> 00:11:44,600
Oh, my dear wife!

239
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,080
Brilliant.

240
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:51,879
Truly brilliant.

241
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,480
What fun. Only you could pull it off.

242
00:11:58,799 --> 00:12:00,840
Do not joke about being a bastard son.

243
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:02,960
Now that you mention it,

244
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,080
I am tempted to take a sworn father.

245
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:05,440
Father is right here.

246
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:06,120
I shall bear witness.

247
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:07,440
Are you ill? You, you...

248
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,480
You are taking advantage of me.

249
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:09,440
How comforting.

250
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,399
Honestly.

251
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,559
Just teasing.

252
00:12:15,799 --> 00:12:16,200
Old Gao,

253
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,399
sorry for tarnishing your name.

254
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,519
That is nothing at all.

255
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:21,399
Actually, his wife,

256
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,279
she would not be too bad.

257
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:30,399
Let us go.

258
00:12:30,759 --> 00:12:32,879
Pack up and return to the capital.

259
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,440
Back to the capital. Move!
